<H3> <TI>   Rakhmonov Leaves for CIS Assembly in St Petersburg </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Rakhmonov Leaves for CIS Assembly in St Petersburg </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0706084894 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Tajik 0800 
GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0706084894 </F>
<F P=104>  Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network </F>
<F P=105>  Tajik </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Emomali Rakhmonov, head of state and chairman of the 
Tajikistan Supreme Soviet, left today for St. Petersburg to 
attend a session of the CIS interparliamentary assembly. 
  Emomali Rakhmonov was seen off at Dushanbe Airport by 
Abdujalil Samadov, chairman of the Council of Ministers of the 
Republic of Tajikistan; Koimdodov, deputy chairman of the 
Republic's Supreme Soviet; the chairmen of the Supreme Soviet 
committees; the deputy chairmen of the Council of Ministers; and 
Senkevich, ambassador extraordinary and plenipotentiary of the 
Russian Federation to Tajikistan. 

