<H3> <TI>   `Rumors' of Special Unit's Return to FCS Denied </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Rumors' of Special Unit's Return to FCS Denied </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM0606154794 Moscow NOVAYA YEZHEDNEVNAYA GAZETA in Russian 4 
Jun 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> PM0606154794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow NOVAYA YEZHEDNEVNAYA GAZETA </F>
