<F P=106> [Investigations Department report under the "Rumors" rubric: </F>
"`Vympel' Stays at the MVD"] 
  [Text] The rumors that have appeared that "Vympel" is 
returning to the FCS [Federal Counterintelligence Service] have 
been greatly exaggerated. There has been no talk of this, and 
nobody has even had such a thought, so the press services of the 
MVD [Ministry of Internal Affairs] and the FCS have declared. 
Moreover, "Vympel" does not exist as such. Following the 
special group's transfer to the MVD, the "Vega" special subunit 
was created on its basis. 
  Work is now being conducted within the FCS itself to create 
its own operational administration. The FCS Press Service does 
not possess any more detailed information at present. 

