<H3> <TI>   AL-QUDS Weekly Banned For `Anti-Jewish Propaganda' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    AL-QUDS Weekly Banned For `Anti-Jewish Propaganda' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0606113194 Tehran IRNA in English 1103 GMT 6 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0606113194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran IRNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Moscow, June 6, IRNA -- Russian authorities have 
banned Moscow-based weekly AL-QUDS for alleged violation of 
Russian laws and printing of anti-Zionist articles. Officials 
cite anti-Jewish propaganda and anti-government stance of the 
weekly as reasons for its ban. 
  The weekly was viewed by political parties and people as a 
prestigious publication which criticized the government, 
revealed plots of Zionism and imperialism and published 
documents relating to the last year's government troop attack on 
parliament. 

</TEXT>

