<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Vesti" newscast] </F>
  [Text] A spokesman for the Bank of Russia says that the 
central bank intends to tighten its control of currency exchange 
points because many contraventions of banking legislation are 
taking place. Among other things, an upper limit will be imposed 
on cash sales of hard currency -- probably this summer. 
However, he added that this question must be agreed with the 
Government and the customs service. 

