  [Text] As we have already reported, President Leonid 
Kravchuk is on a working trip to Kharkov oblast today. This 
morning he met workers of the Kharkov tractor plant. This 
enterprise, one of the largest in the machine-building complex, 
is under threat of stoppage. Managers of agricultural 
machine-building enterprises supplying the Kharkov tractor plant 
(?also) spoke at a consultation on ways for this and other such 
