  [Text] Tashkent, 6 Jun (ITAR-TASS) -- Kim Yong-sam, 
president of the Republic of Korea, issued a warning to the DPRK 
today over the North Korean nuclear problem. Speaking to 
journalists in Tashkent, he said: "I warn North Korea that any 
