<H3> <TI>   President Creates Security Ministry Border Guard </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    President Creates Security Ministry Border Guard </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0706082194 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0755 GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0706082194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by a TIA "KHOVAR" correspondent for TASS] </F>
  [Text] Dushanbe 7 June TASS -- Tajikistan is creating its 
own security ministry frontier guards. A decree to this effect 
has been signed by Tajik President Emomali Rakhmonov. 
  The frontier troops are being created on the base of the 
state border guard department, military formations of the 
republic's Ministry of Security and by transferring military 
personnel from the armed forces and interior troops. 
  The Tajik Ministry of Security is instructed to work out 
within a three-month period and present its proposals regarding 
the general structure and strength, places of dislocation, a 
plan of building and developing the frontier troops. 
  May 28 will be marked every year as the Frontier Guard Day 
in 
Tajikistan. 

</TEXT>

