<H3> <TI>   Shumeyko Opens St Petersburg Meeting </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shumeyko Opens St Petersburg Meeting </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0806085994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0653 GMT 8 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0806085994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] St. Petersburg June 8 ITAR-TASS -- The Council of 
the Inter-parliamentary Assembly of the Commonwealth of 
Independent States has met for a regular session in the Tauride 
Palace in St. Petersburg. 
  The session is attended by the heads of all parliaments of 
the Commonwealth member-states, except Uzbekistan. 
  In his opening address to the session, Chairman of the 
council Vladimir Shumeyko, who is also head of the Upper Chamber 
of the Russian Federal Parliament reported on the implementation 
of the assembly's earlier resolution on the role of the assembly 
and its function in strengthening the Commonwealth." 
