<H3> <TI>   Russian Border Guards Prevent Illegal Crossings </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Border Guards Prevent Illegal Crossings </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0806093794 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0925 GMT 8 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0806093794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] </F>
  [Text] Dushanbe 8 June TASS -- Russian border troops 
suppressed at least four attempts at illegal crossing of the 
border between Tajikistan and Afghanistan on Tuesday [7 June] 
night. 
  Artillery fire was opened to stop a group of transgressors 
at 
a stretch guarded by the Pyanj unit, and more fire had to be 
used to stop the violation of the border near Sarigora and 
Shuroabad where the Moscow border guard unit is in charge. 
  Up to thirty Tajik armed opposition members were repelled 
when trying to cross the border from Afghanistan into Tajikistan 
in the Pamirs mountains. 
  None of the Russian border troops was injured. 

</TEXT>

