<F P=106> [Report by UKRINFORM correspondent Lev Ryabchikov] </F>
  [Text] Simferopol 7 June TASS -- The Crimean police are not 
transferred in subordination to the Ukrainian Interior 
Ministry's Main Interior Department for the Crimea as it was 
