<H3> <TI>   Working Group Drafts National Security Concept </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Working Group Drafts National Security Concept </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS0906090294 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1715 
GMT 9 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS0906090294 </F>
<F P=104>  Minsk Radio Minsk Network </F>
<F P=105>  Belarusian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] An interdepartmental working group, headed by Deputy 
Prime Minister Syarhey Linh, has drafted a concept of national 
security of Belarus, which was discussed and approved at a 
regular session of the Cabinet of Ministers. The essence of the 
concept of national security of Belarus is the ability of the 
state to protect national values and interests under specific 
exterior and interior conditions. 

</TEXT>

