<H3> <TI>   Russian Air Force Unit Refuses To Clear Mine Fields </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Air Force Unit Refuses To Clear Mine Fields </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS0906102494 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1715 
GMT 8 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS0906102494 </F>
<F P=104>  Minsk Radio Minsk Network </F>
<F P=105>  Belarusian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A former training ground -- situated in the 
(?Krichev) Rayon -- of the 40th Russian Air Force Group has 
caused big problems for the local administration. To use this 
territory in the interests of the rayon, mine clearing, and land 
improvement should be carried out, and the housing of the small 
garrison should be repaired. The rayon executive committee 
addressed the command staff of this unit and the Belarusian 
Defense Ministry asking for help. However, foreign servicemen 
refuse to perform this work. Therefore, the rayon executive 
committee addressed the Mogilev Oblast Executive Committee to 
plead with the Belarusian Government to resolve this issue on an 
intergovernmental level. 

</TEXT>

