<F P=103> LD0806151494 </F>
<F P=104>  Almaty Kazakh Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At its morning plenary session today, the parliament 
approved the agenda for two days. The law on entering 
amendments and additions in the code of administrative breaches 
was adopted on an article-by-article basis, in view of the 
adoption of the law on architecture and urban construction in 
