<H4>    Resignation Rumors `Groundless' </H4>

<F P=102> LD0906115994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1122 GMT 9 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0906115994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
